2ex.com/avatar/1060/7918/344132_mini.png?m=1537245625", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1060/7918/344132_mini.png?m=1537245625", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 344132}, "last_reply_by": "viakiba", "last_touched": 1623042711, "title": "为什么很少听说有人用 kotlin 开发后端", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781828", "created": 1623035654, "content": "相印的 kotlin 后端的招聘岗位也很少，很疑惑，这么好使的后端语言，为什么一直处于较冷的状态。", "content_rendered": "相印的 kotlin 后端的招聘岗位也很少，很疑惑，这么好使的后端语言，为什么一直处于较冷的状态。", "last_modified": 1623035654, "replies": 27, "id": 781828}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1615111825", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1615111825", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 15006, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825", "stars": 1835, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "dcty", "website": "", "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/90ea4f000f92d3e5d23f60a9a358023e?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dcty", "tagline": "", "twitter": null, "created": 1390235372, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/90ea4f000f92d3e5d23f60a9a358023e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/90ea4f000f92d3e5d23f60a9a358023e?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": null, "id": 54616}, "last_reply_by": "lachesis", "last_touched": 1623038708, "title": "苹果调整国行 AppleCare+ 服务政策", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781791", "created": 1623028633, "content": "苹果调整了国行 AppleCare+ 服务政策，线上购买的机型原先是自购买日起算 60 天内都可以加购 AC+ 服务，现在调整过后是只有 7 天时间可以加购 AC+ 服务了。\r\n\r\n而线下购买的机型依然保持 60 天内加购 AC+ 的服务，不过上保需要携带产品先去线下检测，确认产品没有损坏后才可以正常加购。", "content_rendered": "<p>苹果调整了国行 AppleCare+ 服务政策，线上购买的机型原先是自购买日起算 60 天内都可以加购 AC+ 服务，现在调整过后是只有 7 天时间可以加购 AC+ 服务了。</p>\n<p>而线下购买的机型依然保持 60 天内加购 AC+ 的服务，不过上保需要携带产品先去线下检测，确认产品没有损坏后才可以正常加购。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1623028633, "replies": 27, "id": 781791}]